    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Tadpole of Xenophrys serchhipii (Stage 35); (A) Lateral view; (B) Dorsal view; (C) Ventral view (scale bar = 10 mm); (D) Oral disc, dorsal view (scale bar = 1 mm)." ;
